/*
File purpose:
This file contains openHAB automation rules for the safety-monitoring project.

Current rule:
When PIR motion is detected, openHAB toggles the relay if automation is enabled.
*/

// Rule name shown in logs.
rule "Motion toggles relay"
when
    // Trigger: run this rule when the Motion item changes to ON.
    Item Motion changed to ON
then
    // Only run the relay action if the local automation switch is enabled.
    if (MotionAutomation.state == ON) {
        // If the relay is currently ON, switch it OFF.
        if (Relay.state == ON) {
            Relay.sendCommand(OFF)
        // Otherwise, switch it ON.
        } else {
            Relay.sendCommand(ON)
        }
    }
end
